    <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/list/23067.Dan_Barker">Books by Dan   Barker</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
